{"thag10.1:0.1":"Theragatha 10.1 ","thag10.1:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","thag10.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag10.1:0.4":"Kaludayittheragatha ","thag10.1:1.1":"“Angarino dani duma bhadante, ","thag10.1:1.2":"Phalesino chadanam vippahaya; ","thag10.1:1.3":"Te accimantova pabhasayanti, ","thag10.1:1.4":"Samayo mahavira bhagi rasanam. ","thag10.1:2.1":"Dumani phullani manoramani, ","thag10.1:2.2":"Samantato sabbadisa pavanti; ","thag10.1:2.3":"Pattam pahaya phalamasasana, ","thag10.1:2.4":"Kalo ito pakkamanaya vira. ","thag10.1:3.1":"Nevatisitam na panatiunham, ","thag10.1:3.2":"Sukha utu addhaniya bhadante; ","thag10.1:3.3":"Passantu tam sakiya koliya ca, ","thag10.1:3.4":"Pacchamukham rohiniyam tarantam. ","thag10.1:4.1":"Asaya kasate khettam, ","thag10.1:4.2":"bijam asaya vappati; ","thag10.1:4.3":"Asaya vanija yanti, ","thag10.1:4.4":"samuddam dhanaharaka; ","thag10.1:4.5":"Yaya asaya titthami, ","thag10.1:4.6":"sa me asa samijjhatu. ","thag10.1:5.1":"Punappunam ceva vapanti bijam, ","thag10.1:5.2":"Punappunam vassati devaraja; ","thag10.1:5.3":"Punappunam khettam kasanti kassaka, ","thag10.1:5.4":"Punappunam dhannamupeti rattham. ","thag10.1:6.1":"Punappunam yacanaka caranti, ","thag10.1:6.2":"Punappunam danapati dadanti; ","thag10.1:6.3":"Punappunam danapati daditva, ","thag10.1:6.4":"Punappunam saggamupenti thanam. ","thag10.1:7.1":"Viro have sattayugam puneti, ","thag10.1:7.2":"Yasmim kule jayati bhuripanno; ","thag10.1:7.3":"Mannamaham sakkati devadevo, ","thag10.1:7.4":"Taya hi jato muni saccanamo. ","thag10.1:8.1":"Suddhodano nama pita mahesino, ","thag10.1:8.2":"Buddhassa mata pana mayanama; ","thag10.1:8.3":"Ya bodhisattam parihariya kucchina, ","thag10.1:8.4":"Kayassa bheda tidivamhi modati. ","thag10.1:9.1":"Sa gotami kalakata ito cuta, ","thag10.1:9.2":"Dibbehi kamehi samangibhuta; ","thag10.1:9.3":"Sa modati kamagunehi pancahi, ","thag10.1:9.4":"Parivarita devaganehi tehi”. ","thag10.1:10.1":"“Buddhassa puttomhi asayhasahino, ","thag10.1:10.2":"Angirasassappatimassa tadino; ","thag10.1:10.3":"Pitupita mayham tuvamsi sakka, ","thag10.1:10.4":"Dhammena me gotama ayyakosi”ti. ","thag10.1:10.5":"… Kaludayi thero …. "}